-=head1 Cryptography
-
-A complete description of RT's cryptography capabilities can be found in
-L<RT::Crypt>. At this moment, GnuPG (PGP) and SMIME security protocols are
-supported.
-
-=over 4
-
-=item C<%Crypt>
-
-The following options apply to all cryptography protocols.
